2. Enter Call Type (e.g., "10-50 Traffic Accident")
3. Specify Location (address/intersection)
4. Add Caller Information (if available)
5. Write Initial Narrative
6. Set Priority Level (Low/Medium/High)
7. Submit to create incident</pre>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

